                     <interp inst="t18240407-91-person895" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The brush is my father's, and I believe the scissars to be so; the whip is his. I manage the business in Bond-street. The lowest value of the six large table-knives and forks is 6 l. The value of the lot he said he sold to the Jew for 1 l. 19 s. is 5 l. 4 s.</p>

               <p>The prisoner made no defence.</p>
